      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented version control, regression testing, and release validation for blood-pump flow applications.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used with documented QA records including regression test suite and release notes confirming hemolysis-relevant turbulence model validation. Required level 2 met."
    },
    {
